text: Mark Harry Diones (born March 1, 1993) is a triple jumper from the Philippines. In 2017 he won silver medals at the Asian Championships and Southeast Asian Games. He placed 12th at the 2018 Asian Games. ==References== Category:Filipino male triple jumpers Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2018 Asian Games Category:Southeast Asian Games silver medalists for the Philippines Category:Southeast Asian Games medalists in athletics Category:Competitors at the 2017 Southeast Asian Games Category:Asian Games competitors for the Philippines Category:Competitors at the 2019 Southeast Asian Games
